metadata.name: Path of Curiosity
metadata.description:
When you feel like you have lost your way... find yourself, enjoy the mystery of not knowing what's next, embrace adventure, experience something new, forge friendships. Push through your fears and follow the path of curiosity... 

Featuring cameos of MUMBOT WORLD characters Girl From the Forest Floor, Shumi Mushrumi, Mossy, Cryspu, Marudo, Skully B., Aughostus and more. This artwork includes prompts hidden throughout representing part of a daily Aughostus themed drawing prompt during the month of August which I host annually. 

Graphite on paper

1878  px ×  2691 px at 300 dpi
